N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 95.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

As used in these regulations the term race meeting includes
both harness race meetings and other horse race meetings, and the word licensee
means any corporation or association duly licensed by the State Racing and

Wagering Board to conduct any such race meeting. Notes
